data.description: Discover a fantastic investment opportunity or your ideal starter home in this well-priced gem! Renovated just 4 years ago, this residence offers modern comfort and style. Situated on a large lot with alley access, it provides both convenience and potential. Perfectly positioned near Interstate 8, this home combines affordability and accessibility. Contact us soon before it's sold! (pictures are from when the home was last remodeled, normal wear and tear after 4 years)
